），總之一彈上185、186蚊嗰啲位就沽，博呢浸落去嘅。 過年返o黎之後個市先有明確方向㗎喇，聽日、後日朝早半日市都有機會挾一挾倉嘅，但係幅度可能未必會太大嘅。"},{"pid":"eb060629f1dd6f35adf63c9699dd7b229c6b19fe","tid":112330,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"肛交所做咩升左成10點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cfecd8245afbf458f7a5ebf9964f4b31fd608b","tid":112330,"uid":1485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"多謝大師，200都黎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253cf11789be0974d7a6c0af121dabf31f789324","tid":112330,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"23400熊仔已斬殺，師父神人也，235阻力位今日有機會揾大師兄打個交叉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6d29f34f9879d7ad50bfef425bc264e9db225c","tid":112330,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝大師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/11dcd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F11dcd7.jpg&h=9feb958b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"872e28a00452cf0fd8e0ffb90ad8040df1a0ae5c","tid":112330,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝大師，200都黎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/af4207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Faf4207.jpg&h=df543151&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4488f1157342cf0854ade2a8bd2342877931227e","tid":112330,"uid":11003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"分分鐘大師今日叫人入港交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae70b2a6d4d7a70e0